com.SIMRacingApps

Class Car.LapType

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.SIMRacingApps.Car.LapType
  • Enclosing class:
    Car

    public static class Car.LapType
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines and validates an enumerated String class of the different types of laps that can be returned by methods that take a LapType as an argument.

        public static java.lang.String getReference(java.lang.String ref)
